What you need to know:  ADAK chief executive officer Sarah Shibutse disclosed Thursday that they have adopted the 2021 Anti-doping Code that now allows them to release the names of those who violate anti-doping rules immediatelyADAK had to go through appeals among other legal processes before they published the names of those affectedShibutse said since the start of their calendar in July last year, they have suspended 20 sportsmen and women mostly from athletics with a couple coming from football and body-building